{
  "page": "Scourge",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Scourge.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/Scourge.jpg/350px-Scourge.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"232\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/6/60/Scourge.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Scourge.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Scourge, by Franz Miklis © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Scourge</b> is a river in southern <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dorne.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dorne and the location of the Scourge\"><img alt=\"Dorne and the location of the Scourge\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/400px-Dorne.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/600px-Dorne.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/800px-Dorne.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 57.2%; left: 52.8%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"Dorne and the location of the Scourge\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Scourge\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 90%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Scourge</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> and the location of the Scourge\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>It meets the <a href=\"/index.php/Vaith_(river)\" title=\"Vaith (river)\">Vaith</a> in the Dornish eastern mountains to form the <a href=\"/index.php/Greenblood\" title=\"Greenblood\">Greenblood</a> near <a href=\"/index.php/Godsgrace\" title=\"Godsgrace\">Godsgrace</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scourge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones_(game)\" title=\"A Game of Thrones (game)\">A Game of Thrones RPG and Resource Book</a>, Guardians of Order</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Map_of_the_South\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Map of the South\">Map of the South</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\